column4: NSLOCTEXT("[9E19DCFF4DE032B23EBF57A168D5A489]", "25C0750B426763CEEB60DB9901E0CEE4", "I used to live in the city. You smell like the city.")
NSLOCTEXT("[9E19DCFF4DE032B23EBF57A168D5A489]", "4FCB11BF448E793F719A8F8CB3A50714", "It\'s scary. I left the city and lost my memory.")
NSLOCTEXT("[9E19DCFF4DE032B23EBF57A168D5A489]", "E9AD3836459EF5950A753F9097123874", "But thanks to you, I remember everything now.")
NSLOCTEXT("[9E19DCFF4DE032B23EBF57A168D5A489]", "267C9906487FE74BE64D42979EF65477", "I\'m going back to the city, OK?")
NSLOCTEXT("[9E19DCFF4DE032B23EBF57A168D5A489]", "5C15A227465BE0B897C6EDA0550268B8", "Of course. I\'m sure the city is now more lively than before.")
